     * Initializes a generator object which is associated with a static
     * D function.  The function will be called once to prepare the range
     * for iteration.
     *
     * Params:
     *  fn = The fiber function.
     *
     * In:
     *  fn must not be null.
     */
    this(void function() fn)
    {
        super(fn);
        call();
    }

